Family communication: We prioritize clear, frequent updates. Families typically receive regular check-ins (highlights of the day, meals/rest notes as relevant, and any important moments), and we’re proactive if a child needs extra support with adjustment or behavior. We also offer scheduled conferences and are available for brief chats at drop-off/pick-up, with longer meetings by appointment.
